These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
Movie-Genre: epic, musical
Birthday: april, november
1. Movie-Genre:epic is on the left of Birthday:april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | musical |
| Birthday     | november | april  |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
Game: mah-jongg, go
Sport: skateboarding, snowboarding
1. Game:go is on the right of Sport:skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Game    | mah-jongg      | go         |
| Sport   | skateboarding | snowboarding |

 #################################
 
